[urgent]: mostly needs prose tidy-up, and some relaxng schema
examples: needed for Fabio's book: [SB by 31 Jul] </li><li><a name="id2284676"></a>Revise ST: in particular <ul><li><a name="id2284681"></a>overhaul discussion of class system</li><li><a name="id2284685"></a>add new material about  proposed new core modules</li></ul> </li><li><a name="id2284691"></a>Review HD and update its metadata discussion: consolidate and
move discussion of other metadata schemes in current HD and IH; review
